    <item>
      <title>迈克·威尔逊预计 2025 年上半年市场波动较大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-08/mike-wilson-expects-choppy-first-half-of-2025-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利首席美国股票策略师迈克·威尔逊 (Mike Wilson) 预计 2025 年上半年市场波动较大，下半年市场将有所改善。他密切关注华盛顿的贸易和关税情况，并表示他仍然看好金融业。他在“彭博监视”节目中发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-08/mike-wilson-expects-choppy-first-half-of-2025-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 14:11:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国经济：每周申请失业救济人数降至 201,000</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-08/us-economy-weekly-jobless-claims-sink-to-201-000-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周美国失业救济申请人数减少 10,000 人至 201,000 人，降至 2 月以来的最低水平。迈克尔·麦基在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-08/us-economy-weekly-jobless-claims-sink-to-201-000-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 13:57:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储沃勒认为进一步降息“将是适当的”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-08/fed-s-waller-believes-further-cuts-will-be-appropriate-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事克里斯托弗·沃勒表示，“如果前景像我在这里描述的一样发展，我将支持在 2025 年继续下调我们的政策利率”，因为他相信通胀将继续降温至央行 2% 的目标。沃勒还对关税会对通胀产生重大影响的说法表示怀疑，称关税“不太可能影响我对适当货币政策的看法”。周三，他在经济合作与发展组织 (OECD) 的一次活动上发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-08/fed-s-waller-believes-further-cuts-will-be-appropriate-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 13:49:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国主要国债收益率有望达到 2023 年峰值，达到 5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/key-us-treasury-yields-approach-2023-peaks-with-5-in-sight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀焦虑引发的抛售席卷全球债券市场，10 年期美国国债收益率跃升至 2023 年底以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/key-us-treasury-yields-approach-2023-peaks-with-5-in-sight</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 13:40:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>桥水基金扩大中国领先地位，资产规模在艰难的一年中增长 40%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/bridgewater-widens-china-lead-on-40-asset-jump-in-tough-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[桥水基金的多元资产策略凭借其稳定的回报，在动荡的市场中吸引了更多富有的本地客户，去年在中国进一步扩大了对全球同行的领先优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/bridgewater-widens-china-lead-on-40-asset-jump-in-tough-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 13:10:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储官员沃勒支持进一步降息，称通胀正在下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/fed-s-waller-supports-further-cuts-says-inflation-moving-lower</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事克里斯托弗·沃勒表示，他相信通胀将继续降温至央行2%的目标，这促使他支持今年进一步降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/fed-s-waller-supports-further-cuts-says-inflation-moving-lower</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言禁止建造风电厂 导致风电份额暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/trump-spurs-wind-power-share-slump-after-taking-aim-at-windmills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示他的目标是上任后在美国不再建造新的风车，随后欧洲一些最大的风力发电公司的股价于周三下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/trump-spurs-wind-power-share-slump-after-taking-aim-at-windmills</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 10:37:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>库存紧缩导致油价突破每桶 75 美元后企稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于一份行业报告指出美国原油库存再次下降，纽约油价近三个月来首次突破每桶 75 美元后企稳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 23:33:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：债券市场在暴跌后企稳，股市止跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受美国国债收益率飙升和美联储在通胀压力下放慢降息步伐的猜测推动，股市停止了下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 22:33:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
